{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Immerse yourself in <strong>LEAVE</strong>, a narrative-driven platformer and atmospheric adventure that tells a deeply moving story of survival, resilience, and the fight for freedom. Follow the journey of a young child navigating the haunting beauty of a world torn apart by tyranny, experiencing themes of hope, defiance, and the devastating impact of oppression all brought to life through cinematic visuals, emotional storytelling, and seamless gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417200/extras/Leave_s-Innovative-Mechanics.gif?t=1737030682\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Solve intricate puzzles using interactive systems like pushing objects, breaking obstacles with an axe, and crawling under carpets to evade enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Engage with procedural animations and active rag-doll physics for immersive movement and realistic interactions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experiment with fun activities like throwing rocks into a lake or playfully interacting with the world around you.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417200/extras/Leave_s-Dynamic-and-Interactive-World.gif?t=1737030682\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore a beautifully crafted 3D environment with a fixed, adaptive camera that enhances your perspective based on the child\u2019s experiences and surroundings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417200/extras/Leave_s-Seamless-Cinematic-Experience.gif?t=1737030682\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enjoy a continuous cinematic experience with no loading screens or interruptions, blending gameplay and storytelling into a movie-like flow.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417200/extras/Leave_s-Social-Interactions.gif?t=1737030682\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build connections with NPCs in the game world through meaningful interactions, from waving at familiar faces to engaging with merchants in the market.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417200/extras/Leave_s-Atmospheric-World_-Sound_-and-Music.gif?t=1737030682\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Immerse yourself in a movie-like journey where the game\u2019s atmospheric world, paired with expertly crafted sound and music, amplifies every moment and deepens your emotional connection to the story.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Customizable Experience:</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Tailor graphics settings, control layouts, and more for a personalized and accessible gaming experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore, play, and uncover the secrets of this poignant and powerful world. With its unique art style, impactful narrative, and innovative mechanics, <strong>LEAVE</strong> promises an unforgettable adventure that resonates with players of all ages.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417200/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737030682","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417200/page.bg.jpg?t=1737030682","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417200/c7340313d94dc45cb736630ecec1fde8cb907051/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737030682","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417200/c7340313d94dc45cb736630ecec1fde8cb907051/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737030682","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full c